        MAY_IT_SERVE_TO_ALWAYS_KEEP_WINDURST_NEAR                             = 8196,  -- May it serve to always keep Windurst near to your heart.
        I_AM_AFRAID_YOU_VE_NO_ROOM_TO                                         = 8197,  -- I am afraid you've no room to carry any more possessions. Do not worry. I shall have it delivered to the Cobra post, where you may pick it up at your convenience.
        IT_IS_A_JOYOUS_DAY_FOR_MY_WINDURST                                    = 8198,  -- It is a joyous day, for my Windurst is truly blessed with the most steadfast of friends. May our era of peace and harmony abide for ages to come.
        YOU_AS_WELL_PROMISE_ME_THAT_WHEREVER_YOUR                             = 8199,  -- You as well, %. Promise me that wherever your travels may lead you, you will always consider Windurst your second home.
        THIS_TERRIBLE_WAR_HAS_LEFT_COUNTLESS_SHATTERED_HOPES                  = 8200,  -- This terrible war has left countless shattered hopes and dreams in its wake. But one by one, we shall piece them together.
        FOR_IT_IS_YOU_ALL_OF_YOU_WHO                                          = 8201,  -- For it is you--all of you--who shall lead us into the future. As long as you believe, and hold us in your heart...this world will forever endure.
        THE_FEDERATION_OF_WINDURST_AN_ANCIENT_CAPITAL_NURTURED                = 8202,  -- The Federation of Windurst... An ancient capital nurtured by the boughs of a great tree, blessed by magical waters, and protected by the moon and stars...
        IN_A_TIME_FORGOTTEN_A_PEOPLE_FORCED_TO                                = 8203,  -- In a time forgotten, a people forced to wander by starvation and cold were led to this land by a wondrous star...
        LOST_SOULS_ADRIFT_IN_TIME_FOUND_THEMSELVES_WITHIN                     = 8204,  -- Lost souls, adrift in time, found themselves within these walls, and many a tear was shed...
        THOSE_TEARS_NOURISHED_THE_SOIL_AND_TODAY_A                            = 8205,  -- Those tears nourished the soil, and today, a sapling of hope peeks through the earth to meet a bright new sun...
        SHRINK_NOT_FROM_YOUR_FUTURE_MY_FRIEND                                 = 8206,  -- Shrink not from your future, my friend...
        FOR_EVEN_THE_LONGEST_DARKEST_NIGHT_MUST_EVENTUALLY                    = 8207,  -- For even the longest, darkest night must eventually give way to the dawn.
        AND_THOUGH_YOUR_BODY_MAY_RETURN_TO_THE                                = 8208,  -- And though your body may return to the earth, your memory shall live on. In the wind, the trees, and the hearts of those whose lives you shared...
        YOUR_DESTINY_IS_YOURS_ALONE_TO_FORGE_FOR                              = 8209,  -- Your destiny is yours alone to forge. For this is neither the beginning nor the end, but merely one stop on a journey of limitless possibilities...
        THE_SAPLING_SHALL_GROW_INTO_A_GREAT_TREE                              = 8210,  -- The sapling shall grow into a great tree. Its leaves will take to the wind, carrying hopes and dreams with them, and a new chapter of history will be written.
        BUT_THAT_IS_A_STORY_FOR_ANOTHER_TIME                                  = 8211,  -- ...But that is a story for another time.
        ANOTHER_DAY_WHEN_THE_STARS_IN_THE_HEAVENS                             = 8212,  -- Another day, when the stars in the heavens align to bring our paths together once more...
        THERE_YOU_ARE_IF_YOU_RE_LOOKING_FOR                                   = 8213,  -- There you are, %. If you're looking for your %, I've got it right here.
        I_VE_GOTTA_SAY_JUST_LOOKIN_AT_IT                                      = 8214,  -- I've gotta say, just lookin' at it puts a big grrrin on my face. You're going to wanna keep this safe, you hear?
        WHAT_THE_I_VE_NEVER_SEEN_A_BAG                                        = 8215,  -- What the...? I've never seen a bag so full o' junk. Come back when you've strrraightened it out, will ya?
        IF_IT_ISN_T_OUR_STAR_MERCENARY_WHY                                    = 8216,  -- If it isn't our star mercenary, %! Why, just by seeing you around I know that the Federation is in good hands.
        COURSE_THE_REST_OF_US_WON_T_BE                                        = 8217,  -- 'Course, the rest of us won't be letting up our guarrrd, either. Any Yagudo stragglers within a malm of the capital are gonna be in for a worrrld o' hurt!
        OBTAINED_5                                                            = 8218,  -- % obtained %.
        OH_THERE_YOU_ARE                                                      = 8219,  -- Oh, %, there you are!
        AND_NOT_A_MOMENT_TOO_SOON_MASTER_LEHKO                                = 8220,  -- ...And not a moment too soon. Master Lehko has been searrrching all over for you!
        NONE_TOO_EASY_A_TASK_I_MIGHT_ADD                                      = 8221,  -- None too easy a task, I might add, what with everyone in the city rrrunning around like cockatrices with their heads cut off. It's utter chaos, I tell you!
        WHAT_HAVEN_T_YOU_HEARD_JUST_LOOK                                      = 8222,  -- What, haven't you heard? Just look!
        HEAR_YE_HEAR_YE_CITIZENS_OF_WINDURST                                  = 8223,  -- Hear ye, hear ye! Citizens of Windurst!
        DUE_TO_IMMINENT_DANGER_OF_A_BEASTMAN_ATTACK                           = 8224,  -- Due to imminent danger of a beastman attack, the Federation has declared a state of high alertaru!
        ALL_NON_MILITARY_PERSONNEL_ARE_HEREBY_ORDERED_TO                      = 8225,  -- All non-military personnel are hereby ordered to take sheltaru indoors until further-wurther notice. I repeataru, this is not a drill!
        THERRRE_YOU_HAVE_IT_CIVILIANS_HAVE_BEEN_ORDERED                       = 8226,  -- Therrre you have it. Civilians have been ordered off the streets, and all mercenaries are to ready for battle immediately.
        WITH_THE_ENEMY_READY_TO_STRRRIKE_AT_ANY                               = 8227,  -- With the enemy ready to strrrike at any moment, one can never be too ready. Have you seen to your preparations?
        NEED_YOU_EVEN_ASK_WHY_AJIDO_MARUJIDO_CHILD                            = 8228,  -- Need you even ask!? Why, Ajido-Marujido, Child Genius, is ever ready for anything those filthy-wilthy-feathered goons could throw at us!
        WHAT_THE_ARE_YOU_OUT_OF_YOUR_GOURRRD                                  = 8229,  -- What the--!? Are you out of your gourrrd, you little brat!? Get back inside! If the city comes under attack, you'll break more than just the rims of those rrridiculous glasses!
        HAH_LIKE_I_D_ENTRUST_THE_DEFENSE_OF                                   = 8230,  -- Hah! Like I'd entrust the defense of the Federation to a mangy-wangy lot like you! Behold the valiantaru sorcerers and swordswomen of the Windurstian Teen Force (WTF), under the capable command of Warlock-Warlord-in-Waiting Ajido-Marujido!
        NOW_IF_YOU_LL_EXCUSE_US_WE_HAVE                                       = 8231,  -- Now if you'll excuse us, we have an important audience with the big cheese himself--er, even if he doesn't know it yetaru. Someone has to save our glorious nation while you strays stand around swatting insects with your tails!
        DANGER_ANGER_TARGETASREACHEDUTHORIZEDERIMETER                         = 8232,  -- DaNGer!ANgeR! TaRGeTaSREaCHeDUTHoRiZeDErImETeR!
        CEASENDESIST_INITIATINGECOVERYROCEDURE                                = 8233,  -- CeASeNDeSIsT! INiTiaTiNGeCOVeRyrOCeDuRE!
        WH_WHAT_UNHANDY_WAND_ME_YOU_CONFOUNDED_CONTRAPTION                    = 8234,  -- Wh-what!? Unhandy-wand me, you confounded contraption!
        THIS_IS_THAT_STUT_DOODLY_UTTERING_OLD_KORU                            = 8235,  -- This is that stut-doodly-uttering old Koru-Moru's doing! Blastaru it! When the Federation falls, he'll rue the day he detained its would-be hero!
        I_SAID_PUT_ME_DOWN_YOU_HAM_HANDED                                     = 8236,  -- I said put me down, you ham-handed heap of--uwaaaaaaaaahhh!
        OH_DEARRR_WELL_THAT_SHOULD_TEACH_THE_BOY                              = 8237,  -- Oh dearrr. Well, that should teach the boy a lesson about getting too big for his brrreeches.
        AT_ANY_RATE_YOU_D_BEST_HURRRY_ALONG                                   = 8238,  -- At any rate, %, you'd best hurrry along. Master Lehko's waiting in Heavens Tower, and I hear he has an especially imporrrtant assignment for you this time.
        YOU_RRRE_STILL_STANDING_AROUND_HERE_MASTER_LEHKO                      = 8239,  -- %! You'rrre still standing around here? Master Lehko's waiting for you in Heavens Tower with a special assignment. Now hurry along!
        WELL_IF_IT_ISN_T_OUR_STALWART_YOU                                     = 8240,  -- Well, if it isn't our stalwart %! You're always a sightaru for sore eyes.
        WITH_THE_BEASTMEN_DRAWING_EVER_NEARER_IT_S                            = 8241,  -- With the beastmen drawing ever nearer, it's absolutaru madness around here. But please, don't let me keepy-weep you. Master Lehko awaits within.
        AH_ALWAYS_A_PLEASURE_COME_IN_CURRRL_UP                                = 8242,  -- Ah, %! Always a pleasure. Come in, currrl up and make yourself comforrrtable.
        A_BIT_LONELY_IN_HERE_TODAY_YOU_SAY                                    = 8243,  -- A bit lonely in here today, you say? Indeed it is.
        WITH_THE_WARLOCK_WARLORD_PERRRSONALLY_LEADING_THE_VALDEAUNIAN         = 8244,  -- With the Warlock Warlord perrrsonally leading the Valdeaunian expedition, I fearrr I've only my own poor company to offer you today.
        BUT_FORGIVE_ME_IF_I_CUT_SHORT_THE                                     = 8245,  -- But forgive me if I cut short the pleasantrrries. %, I require your aid in a most vital operrration.
        TO_WIT_I_M_EXPECTING_A_PAIR_OF                                        = 8246,  -- To wit, I'm expecting a pair of parrrticularly important guests, and they're in need of an escort. ...And, should the circumstances demand it, a bodyguard.
        TWO_MITHRAN_WAYFARERS_FROM_THE_HOMELAND_TO_BE                         = 8247,  -- Two Mithran wayfarers from the homeland, to be prrrecise. I've just received word that they've arrived safely on Mindartian shores.
        THEY_SHOULD_BE_ARRIVING_AT_THE_RRRENDEZVOUS_POINT                     = 8248,  -- They should be arriving at the rrrendezvous point--the monument that stands on Fort Karugo-Narugo's western embankment--before long. Can I trrrust you to see them safely back here?
        I_D_GO_MYSELF_BUT_AS_YOU_MIGHT                                        = 8249,  -- I'd go myself, but as you might imagine, I have my hands quite full rrreadying the mercenaries and devising a sound strrrategy for the city's defense.
        MOTHERLAND_MITHRA_TEND_TO_BE_DISTRRRUSTFUL_SORTS_AS                   = 8250,  -- Motherland Mithra tend to be distrrrustful sorts, as likely to rend the throat of an interloper as give them the time of day. But don't worry. A mention of my name should be enough to keep their claws sheathed.
        AT_LEAST_I_PRRRAY_AS_MUCH_FOR_YOUR                                    = 8251,  -- ...At least I prrray as much, for your sake. Ha-ha!
        HMM_WHAT_MAKES_YOU_THE_LUCKY_MAN_WOMAN                                = 8252,  -- Hmm? What makes you the lucky man/woman] for the job, you ask?
        WHY_YOU_VE_SEEN_HOW_JEALOUS_MY_GIRLS                                  = 8253,  -- Why, you've seen how jealous my girls get every time I grace a member of the fairer sex with a glance. If they discovered that I'd perrrsonally invited two lovely ladies to my humble abode, why, the ensuing battle would send shivers up the spine of the Shadow Lord himself!
        OH_AND_YOU_NEEDN_T_WORRY_MY_FRIENDS                                   = 8254,  -- Oh, and you needn't worry, %. My friends are merrrely business acquaintances, nothing more. <Wink, wink>
        CERTAINLY_A_DASHING_FELLOW_SUCH_AS_YOURSELF_CAN                       = 8255,  -- Certainly, a dashing fellow such as yourself can sympathize with my prrredicament. <Wink, wink>
        ANYWAY_THERE_YOU_HAVE_IT_LET_ME_REMIND                                = 8256,  -- Anyway, there you have it. Let me remind you again that this mission calls for the utmost secrrrecy.
        TAKE_CARE_TO_BE_NEITHER_WITNESSED_NOR_HEARD                           = 8257,  -- Take care to be neither witnessed nor heard by a soul. Least of all the Shadow Lord's minions...or any of your fellow mercenaries of the female perrrsuasion.
        IN_FACT_I_VE_GOT_JUST_THE_WAY                                         = 8258,  -- In fact, I've got just the way for the three of you to keep an especially low prrrofile on your return.
        YOU_RRRECALL_THE_SUBTERRANEAN_PASSAGE_CONNECTING_FORT_KARUGO          = 8259,  -- You rrrecall the subterranean passage connecting Fort Karugo-Narugo with the capital, do you not? The caverns where you helped us stave off the Yagudo onslaught...
        THE_ENTRANCE_LIES_ALONG_THE_WALL_OF_THE                               = 8260,  -- The entrance lies along the wall of the central grrrounds, due east of the rendezvous point. Why don't you lead our guests back through there?
        AND_NOW_IF_YOU_LL_FORGIVE_ME_PRRRESSING                               = 8261,  -- And now, %, if you'll forgive me, prrressing matters elsewhere demand my attention. I'll keep the hearth warm for your return. May the Goddess watch over you!
        SO_THIS_IS_THE_WINDURST_OF_WHICH_I                                    = 8262,  -- So this is the Windurst of which I have heard so much. Such a lush and resplendent nation...'tis a shame to see it so rrravaged by war.
        SNIFF_SNIFF_THE_AIR_SMELLS_PRETTY_LIKE_FRRRESH                        = 8263,  -- <Sniff, sniff> The air smells pretty, like frrresh flowers and leaves. I like it here, Meowmmy!
        AS_DO_I_SYU_BUT_WE_VE_NO                                              = 8264,  -- As do I, Syu. But we've no time to stop and smell the rrroses. Lead us to Lehko, friend.
        IT_S_MY_PLEASURE_TO_WELCOME_YOU_TO                                    = 8265,  -- It's my pleasure to welcome you to Windurst, Nhev Befrathi. Or should I say, Chieftainness...?
        CALL_ME_WHAT_YOU_WILL_A_WOMAN_IN                                      = 8266,  -- Call me what you will. A woman in my position has little use for forrrmalities. This is my daughter, Syu.
        YOU_VE_DONE_WELL_TO_LEAD_MY_FRRRIENDS                                 = 8267,  -- You've done well to lead my frrriends safely here, %. Once again, you prove yourself worthy of all the trrrust I place in you, and then some.
        AND_WITH_THAT_NHEV_LET_US_PRRROCEED_WITH                              = 8268,  -- And with that, Nhev, let us prrroceed with our trrransaction. The item we spoke of--
        IS_HERE                                                               = 8269,  -- ...Is here.
        THE_BOW_OF_LIGHT                                                      = 8270,  -- The Bow of Light...
        NEVER_DID_I_IMAGINE_I_WOULD_GAZE_UPON                                 = 8271,  -- ...Never did I imagine I would gaze upon it again with these two eyes.
        LEHKO_2                                                               = 8272,  -- Lehko...?
        THERE_IS_NO_NEED_FOR_CONCERRRN_NHEV_IS                                = 8273,  -- There is no need for concerrrn, Nhev. % is a friend--a staunch ally who has demonstrated his/her] loyalty time and again.
        PERRRHAPS_YOU_HAVE_HEARD_THE_TALES                                    = 8274,  -- Perrrhaps you have heard the tales, %.
        IT_WAS_SOME_TEN_YEARS_AGO_A_MITHRAN                                   = 8275,  -- It was some ten years ago. A Mithran wayfarer returned to the motherland after a brief sojourn on these shores. She took with her a souvenir acquirrred in her travels: a most currrious stone...
        A_STONE_WHICH_FOR_AGES_HAD_LAIN_SLEEPING                              = 8276,  -- A stone which for ages had lain sleeping in the frrrozen north. A stone possessed of immense and terrrible power...
        THE_TRRRAVELER_S_NAME_WAS_YOW_RABNTAH_AND                             = 8277,  -- The trrraveler's name was Yow Rabntah, and with that stone, she fashioned a bow. An ensorcelled weapon of the most exquisite crrraftsmanship--so beautiful, and so deadly...
        THE_BOW_OF_LIGHT_2                                                    = 8278,  -- ...The Bow of Light.
        IT_IS_WELL_POSSIBLE_THAT_YOW_RABNTAH_HAD                              = 8279,  -- It is well possible that Yow Rabntah had only the purrrest of intentions--that the bow was meant to prrrotect her beloved homeland, and nothing more.
        SADLY_THAT_IS_NOT_WHAT_CAME_TO_PASS                                   = 8280,  -- Sadly, that is not what came to pass. For with its grrreat power came even grrreater temptation.
        TEMPTATION_THAT_PROVED_TOO_STRONG_FOR_HER_OR                          = 8281,  -- ...Temptation that proved too strong for her--or me--to rrresist.
        ID_8282                                                               = 8282,  -- ...
        THE_POWER_THAT_SEETHES_WITHIN_THE_BOW_OF                              = 8283,  -- The power that seethes within the Bow of Light is no ordinary power. It is a force that reaches to the very depths of our souls to wrest forth the fear, the ugliness, that we would deny is there.
        JEALOUSY_DECEIT_HATRRRED_THE_EVILS_THAT_LIE_DORMANT                   = 8284,  -- Jealousy, deceit, hatrrred... The evils that lie dormant within all of us are rrroused and brought to the fore, and we are powerless to resist.
        POWERLESS_INDEED                                                      = 8285,  -- Powerless indeed...
        BEFORE_WE_COULD_REALIZE_WHERE_WE_WENT_ASTRRRAY                        = 8286,  -- Before we could realize where we went astrrray, our verdant home was bathed in the crrrimson of our own blood. Time-nurtured bonds between sister and sister rrripped to shreds like so many scraps of cloth...
        YOW_RABNTAH_WAS_DEEMED_A_SINNER_FOR_HAVING                            = 8287,  -- Yow Rabntah was deemed a sinner for having brought this calamity upon us, and tried for her crimes. As fate would have it, she met her end at the hand of a fiend before her judgment could be passed.
        ID_8288                                                               = 8288,  -- ...
        AS_CHIEFTAINNESS_I_SHARED_RESPONSIBILITY_FOR_THE_SLAUGHTER            = 8289,  -- As Chieftainness, I shared responsibility for the slaughter, and for this sin they hunt me to this very day. Even my daughter--guilty of naught but sharrring my blood--is forced to live the life of a fugitive.
        A_TALE_TO_TUG_AT_THE_HEARTSTRRRINGS_IS                                = 8290,  -- A tale to tug at the heartstrrrings, is it not, %? I thought that by bringing Nhev and Syu to our shores, they could finally live out their lives in peace.
        SADLY_THE_PREDATOR_IS_NOT_SO_EASILY_THROWN                            = 8291,  -- Sadly, the predator is not so easily thrown off the scent. You're acquainted with the Mithran Tracker Shikaree G, are you not? Dispatched from the homeland, she continues to hunt her prrrey with an implacable tenacity that borders on obsession.
        WAS_IT_I_SHARE_WITH_YOU_MY_TALE                                       = 8292,  -- %, was it? I share with you my tale because Lehko assures me that you are a friend. Pray do not betrrray our trust.
        THIS_I_SHALL_TAKE_INTO_MY_CARE                                        = 8293,  -- This, I shall take into my care.
        IT_S_MY_DUTY_AS_MUCH_AS_YOURS                                         = 8294,  -- It's my duty as much as yours to see this dark chapter of our people's historrry to a fitting end.
        BUT_LEHKO                                                             = 8295,  -- But Lehko--
        HAVE_NO_FEAR_NHEV_REALIZING_THE_ERROR_OF                              = 8296,  -- Have no fear, Nhev. Realizing the error of her ways, Yow Rabntah with her dying breath wove a potent incantation to seal the terrible power deep within her creation.
        THAT_SUCH_MEANINGLESS_BLOODSHED_WOULD_NEVER_AGAIN_BE                  = 8297,  -- That such meaningless bloodshed would never again be visited on her prrrecious people...
        THE_SECRET_TO_UNDOING_THE_SEAL_SHE_CARRIED                            = 8298,  -- The secret to undoing the seal, she carried to her grrrave. The bow rrremains, but there is not a living soul who can release its power. Is this not so?
        AYE_YOU_VE_THE_RRRIGHT_OF_IT                                          = 8299,  -- Aye, you've the rrright of it.
        VERY_WELL_I_WAS_PREPARED_TO_DISPOSE_OF                                = 8300,  -- Very well. I was prepared to dispose of it by my own hand, but the task is yours if you would have it. Syu and I have a long road ahead of us still, and 'tis perhaps best we keep the burrrden light.
        INDEED_BEST_THE_TWO_OF_YOU_FIND_SOMEWHERRRE                           = 8301,  -- Indeed. Best the two of you find somewherrre to lie low until the fighting is through. The battlefield that awaits us will be no place for a child...
        I_VE_ORDERED_ALL_FAMILIES_IN_THE_CITY                                 = 8302,  -- I've ordered all families in the city to take up shelter in Windurst Walls. You're more than welcome to a spot among them.
        NO_YOUR_OFFER_IS_KIND_BUT_WE_MUST                                     = 8303,  -- No. Your offer is kind, but we must press on. With the Tracker on the prowl, this place is not safe for us.
        WE_MAKE_FOR_A_CITY_CALLED_JEUNO                                       = 8304,  -- We make for a city called Jeuno.
        A_SOUND_CHOICE_THE_DUCHY_IS_VAST_WITH                                 = 8305,  -- A sound choice. The Duchy is vast, with a citizenry as diverrrse as it is numerous. If there is any place you might succeed in disguising your tracks, it would be there.
        IF_I_COULD_TRRROUBLE_YOU_TO_ESCORT_OUR                                = 8306,  -- %, if I could trrrouble you to escort our guests to--
        THAT_WON_T_BE_NECESSARY_WE_VE_IMPOSED                                 = 8307,  -- That won't be necessary. We've imposed on your friend quite enough already.
        FOR_AS_LONG_AS_OUR_JOURNEY_CONTINUES_WE                               = 8308,  -- For as long as our journey continues, we face it on our own. Farewell, Lehko, %...and thank you.
        LEHKO_TWISTED_THOUGH_ITS_POWER_MAY_BE_THE                             = 8309,  -- ...Lehko. Twisted though its power may be, the bow can summon forth no evil that does not already reside within us.
        I_HAVE_LONG_BELIEVED_THAT_IN_THE_HANDS                                = 8310,  -- I have long believed that in the hands of one pure of heart and strong of will, it could have served its intended purpose...
        ID_8311                                                               = 8311,  -- ...
        THE_STONE_THAT_BROUGHT_RRRUIN_UPON_US_IS                              = 8312,  -- The stone that brought rrruin upon us is born of nature, as are we all. In the end, it is but a mirrror to the soul of its wielder...
        IT_IS_NOT_MY_PLACE_TO_QUESTION_THE                                    = 8313,  -- It is not my place to question the ways of the motherland. But is this truly the Mithran way? To hunt to the ends of the world those who have taken a step astrrray? No matter how true their intentions, no matter how deep their remorse?
        DO_WE_NOT_STRRRIVE_TO_LIVE_IN_HARMONY                                 = 8314,  -- Do we not strrrive to live in harmony with Mother Nature, with each other? No, it does not sit well with me...
        NOR_I_NHEV_NOR_I                                                      = 8315,  -- Nor I, Nhev... Nor I.
        WHAT_TRRRULY_IS_SIN                                                   = 8316,  -- What, trrruly, is sin?
        THOSE_WHO_JUDGE_US_HAVE_FOUND_THEIR_ANSWER                            = 8317,  -- Those who judge us have found their answer. Perhaps someday we sinners will find an answer of our own.
        WHAT_S_THE_MATTER_YOU_LOOK_AS_IF                                      = 8318,  -- What's the matter, %? You look as if you've seen a ghost. Fear not, for this is one bow I haven't the power to bend.
        STILL_IT_NEVER_HURTS_TO_KEEP_A_FEW                                    = 8319,  -- Still, it never hurts to keep a few powerful pieces on hand as the endgame draws near...don't you think?
        AH_HA_BUT_I_JEST_NO_THIS_BOW                                          = 8320,  -- Ah ha, but I jest. No, this bow just holds a cerrrtain sentimental value to me, you see. Given the chance, I simply couldn't let it go.
        AT_ANY_RRRATE_YOU_VE_PROVEN_YOURSELF_A                                = 8321,  -- At any rrrate, you've proven yourself a loyal friend and ally once more. Here, have this % for your trrroubles.
        MEOW_I_VE_GOT_A_PRESENT_FOR_MY                                        = 8322,  -- Meow! I've got a present for my bestest friend! You'll take it, won't you? Pretty pretty please?
        MEOWMMY_AND_I_ARE_GOING_TO_A_PLACE                                    = 8323,  -- Meowmmy and I are going to a place called Jeuno! Come visit us someday, okay?
        OH_FINISHED_YOUR_BUSINESS_WITH_MASTER_LEHKO_I                         = 8324,  -- Oh, %! Finished your business with Master Lehko, I see.
        HM_FRRRIENDS_OF_YOURS                                                 = 8325,  -- Hm? Frrriends of yours, %?
        CURIOUS_I_VE_NOT_SEEN_THEIR_FACES_BEFORE                              = 8326,  -- Curious. I've not seen their faces before...
        HAIL_MERRRCHANT_WHERE_DOES_THE_ROAD_LEAD_YOU                          = 8327,  -- Hail, merrrchant! Where does the road lead you?
        WE_STRRRIKE_FOR_JEUNO                                                 = 8328,  -- We strrrike for Jeuno.
        THE_DUCHY_LIES_IN_SHAMBLES_AFTER_THE_RECENT                           = 8329,  -- The Duchy lies in shambles after the recent beastman attack. Homes rrrazed to the ground, families huddling in the streets as they forrrage for what scraps of food they can find.
        THOUGH_I_FEEL_FOR_THEIR_PLIGHT_I_CANNOT                               = 8330,  -- Though I feel for their plight, I cannot deny that it makes for prrrofitable times for those in my trade. I've even received a substantial order directly from the Ducal Army.
        AN_ERRAND_CALLS_US_TO_JEUNO_AS_WELL                                   = 8331,  -- An errand calls us to Jeuno as well. Could we trrrouble you to take us along?
        AS_YOU_SEE_I_TRAVEL_WITH_MY_CHILD                                     = 8332,  -- As you see, I travel with my child, and the roads these days are not safe for one of her tenderrr years.
        CERRRTAINLY_I_D_WELCOME_THE_COMPANY_YOU_RE                            = 8333,  -- Cerrrtainly! I'd welcome the company. You're a cute little one, aren't ya?
        MEOW_2                                                                = 8334,  -- Meow!
